# Agentic Project

This is a porject for tools of e-studio.

* base tech is described in [package.json](mdc:package.json) follow the existed tech.
* use `tailwind css` for style FIRST.
* use `impress.js` to make presentation cool as presentation tool to work.

The slides generation style is based on 

使用像素风：像素风格UI：使用CSS image-rendering: pixelated 实现像素级完美显示
复古配色：使用16色调色板，如#FF0000红色、#00FF00绿色等经典游戏色
